Name: Energizing Ration
Types: Rations
Components: Smoked Meat, Cracked Pepper, Ashwagandha
Description: These smoked strips send a warm tingling sensation when touched, seeming to encourage the relaxation of muscles and mind alike. When consumed, this ration helps adventurers power through their struggles. Grants a number of temporary HP equal to your Wisdom modifier + your Constitution modifier (minimum of 1). 
